none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Barca, Carles Puyol kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Gerard Pique l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110TQG n\u1eefa. \u1ede Premier League, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 trung v\u1ec7 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/nicolas-hernan-gonzalo-otamendi-50680.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Nicolas Otamendi</strong></span> c\u1ee7a Man City, David Luiz c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Jan Vertonghen c\u1ee7a Tottenham\u2026</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Puyol cho rang Pique la trung ve xuat sac nhat the gioi  hinh anh\" title=\"Puyol cho r\u1eb1ng Pique l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/carles-puyol-chon-ra-hau-ve-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Sergio Ramos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid hay Gerard Pique c\u1ee7a Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ede Italia, Leonardo Bonucci (AC Milan), Giorgio Chiellini (Juventus) c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. Ngo\u00e0i ra v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Thiago Silva c\u1ee7a PSG hay Mats Hummels c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn ra ai xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1edfi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh ri\u00eang.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Carles Puyol ch\u1ecdn Gerard Pique xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Barca, Carles Puyol kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/gerard-pique-44441.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gerard Pique</strong></span> l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i: \u201cC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 gi\u1ecfi tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i Pique l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pique ghi ban cho Barca\" title=\"Pique ghi ban cho Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-barca-41-roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Puyol cho r\u1eb1ng Pique l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 31, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, t\u1eeb kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. Pique \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Pique c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u1ed7 d\u1ef1a tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPuyol c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pique: \u201cKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Roma \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Pique l\u00fac n\u00e0y di chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t tinh t\u1ebf, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Pique x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, anh \u0111ang c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Umtiti l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca </strong></span>\u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0103n 3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gerard Pique \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/770-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gerard Pique \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"855","checkdouble":"183676"},{"date":"06:36 07/04","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 7/4: MU nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby Manchester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/8/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-74-mu-nhan-tin-mung-truoc-tran-derby-manchester.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;fo