.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 7/4.</strong></h2>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>MU nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby Manchester. </strong>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Romero. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, nh\u1eefng Phil Jones, Rojo v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Daley Blind, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 7/4: MU \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby Manchester\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng 74 MU nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc derby h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/Diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-74-MU-nhan-tin-mung-truoc-derby-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 7/4: MU \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby Manchester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Man City ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Cup C1.</strong> Theo HLV Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Man City \u0111\u00e3 thua th\u1ea3m Liverpool 0-3, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Wenger t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. </strong>C\u0169ng trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m t\u1edbi. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Europa League, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi CSKA.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div><strong>Klopp ch\u1eedi fan Liverpool l\u00e0 ngu d\u1ed1t. </strong>\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Man City v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i C\u0110V The Kop \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t x\u1ea5u khi n\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o xe bus c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a fan \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng fan cu\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ngu d\u1ed1t. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xe bus cua Man City bi tan cong\" title=\"Xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/111345-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi fan cu\u1ed3ng Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>MU h\u1ecfi mua sao Monaco.</strong> Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Djibril Sidibe &ndash; h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a AS Monaco. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Antonio Valencia ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"854","checkdouble":"183680"},{"date":"07:48 07/04","title":"Pep: \u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n mua danh hi\u1ec7u\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongd