0\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Brazil, n\u01a1i coi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e0ng nh\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pele c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 25 tu\u1ed5i. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Neymar th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8, trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c, r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, m\u1ed9t Vava ho\u1eb7c Coutinho c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng Pele gi\u00e0nh ngai v\u00e0ng World Cup 1962).&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebft th\u00fac. B\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i so s\u00e1nh, Neymar c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Messi h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar gi\u1ed1ng Messi h\u01a1n Ronaldo\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar gi\u1ed1ng Messi h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&quot;Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar gi\u1ed1ng Messi h\u01a1n Ronaldo&quot;&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ndash;</span>&nbsp;Pele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Neymar lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng \u1edf t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Leo Messi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, khi PSG d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn trong v\u00f2ng 3 th\u00e1ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eeda ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111ang b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c r\u1ea5t nhanh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Cup C1 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn 2 su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi t\u00ean Barca c\u00f9ng Real Madrid. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/voi-messironaldo-ban-gioi-lam-cung-chi-dung-thu-3-184-183029.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/21/voi-messironaldo-ban-gioi-lam-cung-chi-dung-thu-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/voi-messironaldo-ban-gioi-lam-cung-chi-dung-thu-3-184-183029.html\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi Messi-Ronaldo, b\u1ea1n gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil lu\u00f4n mong ch\u1edd t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Carlos th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/neymar-va-psg-khi-chung-ta-khong-thuoc-ve-nhau-184-181902.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/15/neymar-va-psg-khi-chung-ta-khong-thuoc-ve-nhau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/neymar-va-psg-khi-chung-ta-khong-thuoc-ve-nhau-184-181902.html\">Neymar v\u00e0 PSG: Khi ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nhau</span><br>\r\n7 th\u00e1ng tr\u00f4i qua k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 y\u00ean \u1ed5n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil. Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Neymar r\u1eddi PSG...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"852","checkdouble":"183686"},{"date":"10:48 07/04","title":"Xabi Alonso c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/7/xabi-alonso-canh-bao-liverpool-ve-suc-manh-cua-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<html><h