"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuong lai Samuel Umtiti duoc quyet dinh vao cuoi mua giai  hinh anh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/chot-thoi-gian-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-umtiti.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Samuel Umtiti b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Umtiti gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/shaw-duoc-dem-lam-vat-te-than-de-mourinho-mua-sao-barca-172-183111.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>MU quan t\u00e2m Umtiti</strong></span>, Chelsea hay PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Camp Nou. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Samuel Umtiti tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u00f9 m\u1ecbt khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Umtiti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed TBN c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Umtiti quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i hay \u1edf v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/samuel-umtiti-44432.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Samuel Umtiti </strong></span>s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Umtiti\" title=\"Umtiti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/14/Barcelona-Man-Utd-Samuel-Umtiti-918757.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Umtiti ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5, khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. N\u1ebfu trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat gia h\u1ea1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng hay ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf b\u1ea3n giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n, khi \u0111\u00f3 M.U hay Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMessi mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca </strong></span>mua Marquinhos trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Umtiti ra \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng NHM \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n Umtiti ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Umtiti \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/96547-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Umtiti \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"850","checkdouble":"183673"},{"date":"07:52 07/04","title":"Barcelona vs Leganes (01h45 ng\u00e0y 8/4): 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://stat