4px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0ng HLV Valverde v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde khong dam de Messi nghi ngoi hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Valverde kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 Messi ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/hlv-valverde-khong-dam-de-messi-nghi-ngoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Valverde kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 Messi ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/neymar-giong-messi-hon-la-ronaldo-184-183686.html\" target=\"_blank\">Messi</span> \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp khi t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f9ng Argentina h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 3. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho M10 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u00f9ng Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sevilla. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd Messi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c Los Blaugrana \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-2 khi\u1ebfn anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ra tay. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n sau 1 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Valverde ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean Messi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Roma 4-1 \u1edf Champions League. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng v\u1eeba b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Messi ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leganes cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang ta s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3. Messi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. Messi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Barca tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 38 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Real Sociedad \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1979/80. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barcelona-vs-leganes-01h45-ngay-84-3-diem-khong-qua-kho-180-183685.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/Preview-Barca-vs-Leganes.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barcelona-vs-leganes-01h45-ngay-84-3-diem-khong-qua-kho-180-183685.html\">Barcelona vs Leganes (01h45 ng\u00e0y 8/4): 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3</span><br>\r\n<span>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian qua th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Barcelona vs Leganes s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra theo m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u, v\u1edbi...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 san b\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 n\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang d\u1ea7n g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e1i ng\u1ecdt t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"848","checkdouble":"183701"},{"date":"15:16 07/04","title":"Barca \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/15/barca-dang-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.a