0e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luke Shaw</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mua Luke Shaw \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Jordi Alba, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mua Luke Shaw bang duoc o He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Barca mua Luke Shaw b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/15/barca-dang-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mua Luke Shaw \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Lucas Digne t\u1eeb PSG v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Digne \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 20 \u0111\u1ebfn 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Barca ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca </strong></span>h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/luke-shaw-43832.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Luke Shaw</strong></span>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1ebd h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Luke Shaw ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ea3 thi b\u1edfi M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 t\u1edbi Camp Nou v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Luke Shaw l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Luke Shaw th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tottenham, Everton v\u00e0 Newcastle theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Barca l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho Luke Shaw\" title=\"Mourinho Luke Shaw\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/So-vi-pham-luat-cong-bang-tai-chinh,-Barca-hoi-muon-Luke-Shaw-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U do b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Mourinho l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u sao Southampton \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Sport, ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Luke Shaw, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Luke Shaw, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/messi-muon-barca-mua-hau-ve-chelsea-180-182426.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Marcos Alonso</strong></span>. Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/190839-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"847","checkdouble":"183720"},{"date":"16:41 07/04","title":"Ronaldinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Messi cao h\u01a1n Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/7/ronaldinho-danh-gia-messi-cao-hon-ronaldo.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.art