dding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ronaldinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 M10 cao h\u01a1n Cristiano Ronaldo.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Messi cao h\u01a1n Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 10 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cristiano Ronaldo</strong></span> v\u00e0 Lionel Messi l\u00e0 hai ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, h\u1ecd thay nhau gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd ai l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldinho phat bieu ve Lionel Messi khien Ronaldo dau long hinh anh\" title=\"Ronaldinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo \u0111au l\u00f2ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/ronaldinho-danh-gia-messi-cao-hon-ronaldo.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nRonaldinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 M10 cao h\u01a1n Cristiano Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Messi, d\u00f9 th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Messi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng v\u00e0 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Messi qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u, v\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Messi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t 1 ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/lionel-messi-44368.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Lionel Messi</strong></span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh M10 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng: \u201cD\u00f9 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng anh ta c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leo Messi\" title=\"Leo Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/hlv-valverde-khong-dam-de-messi-nghi-ngoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldinho chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 Leo Messi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u0169ng v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u01b0a qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap PSG \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf Champions League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi PSG s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldinho \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, bao g\u1ed3m \u1edf c\u1ea3 c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG, anh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi CLB, \u0110TQG, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/12994-42556/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"846","checkdouble":"183727"},{"date":"14:50 07/04","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! 2 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n thay Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/day-2-nha-cam-quan-duoc-chelsea-dam-phan-thay-conte.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-