nhi\u1ec7m Luis Enrique ho\u1eb7c Max Allegri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Chelsea-sa-thai-Conte-bo-nhiem-Luis-Enrique-hoac-Max-Allegri-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Premier League, Chelsea \u0111ang k\u00e9m Top 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/antonio-conte-147.html\" target=\"_blank\">Conte</span> l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Theo Mirror, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ef7 ph\u00fa ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga mu\u1ed1n c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus l\u00e0m n\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1eeb nay \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Luis Enrique v\u00e0 Max Allegri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Luis Enrique ho\u1eb7c Max Allegri. Theo Sky Sports, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi m\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn 2 HLV n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u1edd h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea dam phan voi Luis Enrique va Max Allegri\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Luis Enrique v\u00e0 Max Allegri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/day-2-nha-cam-quan-duoc-chelsea-dam-phan-thay-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Luis Enrique v\u00e0 Max Allegri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 hai v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd thay th\u1ebf Conte, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn HLV m\u1edbi. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-enrique-chua-den-chelsea-vi-arsenal-172-182328.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Luis Enrique mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal </strong></span>h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Chelsea, c\u1ef1u HLV Barca mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o thay v\u00ec li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay \u0111\u1ed5i HLV nh\u01b0 Chelsea. Ch\u1ec9 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Wenger \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN m\u1edbi c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Max Allegri, d\u00f9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea</span> \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"845","checkdouble":"183719"},{"date":"15:41 07/04","title":"Chelsea nh\u1eadn 2 tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/chelsea-nhan-2-tin-mung-truoc-tran-dau-voi-west-ham.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position