ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/Chelsea-nhan-2-tin-mung-truoc-tran-Chelsea-vs-West-Ham-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Chelsea vs West Ham \u1edf v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, The Blues \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5, h\u1ecd k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u1ebfn 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6 v\u00f2ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0 Tottenham hay Liverpool m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Conte nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea vs West Ham trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eadn 2 tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham, The Blues nh\u1eadn 2 tin vui khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/courtois-thibaut-44363.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Thibaut Courtois </strong></span>v\u00e0 Pedro \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois san sang ra san truoc West Ham\" title=\"Courtois s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/chelsea-nhan-2-tin-mung-truoc-tran-dau-voi-west-ham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPedro c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u1edf Cobham, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u00e0 Pedro r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Chelsea, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham, HLV Conte kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-2-nha-cam-quan-duoc-chelsea-dam-phan-thay-conte-172-183719.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i </strong></span>l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, BL\u0110 Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng sa th\u1ea3i \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia n\u1ebfu Chelsea nh\u1eadn th\u00eam nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"844","checkdouble":"183724"},{"date":"16:07 07/04","title":"Liverpool l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \"r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\" M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/liverpool-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{