 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Cuc-soc-Liverpool-mua-Juan-Mata-voi-gia-30-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Juan Mata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSau 25 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Mata b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt. Mourinho c\u0169ng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m Sanchez hay Lingard \u1edf c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-hy-sinh-sao-khung-de-co-gareth-bale-172-183279.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U quan t\u00e2m Gareth Bale </strong></span>c\u1ee7a Real, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng nh\u1eafm Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Mata. Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Juan Mata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Mata \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Theo Express, Liverpool mua Juan Mata nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Juan Mata\" title=\"Liverpool mua Juan Mata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/liverpool-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Juan Mata \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHLV Klopp \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Mata, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield. The Kop ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 30 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/manchester-united-1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U</strong></span> v\u00e0 Liverpool kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua b\u00e1n, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nhau \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, ngay c\u1ea3 khi The Kop ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nInter Milan c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Mata, v\u00e0 M.U ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn Italia h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Liverpool.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/juan-manuel-mata-garcia-43803.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Mata </strong></span>v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng anh v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Juan Mata \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/28367-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Juan Mata \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"843","checkdouble":"183725"},{"date":"15:31 07/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Stoke vs Tottenham 21h00 ng\u00e0y 7/4 (Premier League 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/truc-tiep-stoke-vs-tottenham-21h00-ngay-74-premier-league-201718.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helv